translation_info: Words between {{}} are variables and must not be translated. Only commands description can be translated. Command ids cannot be changed under any circumstance. Links, names, ids and social media values cannot be translated either. If you have any question please message Todo56#0001 on discord or email todo@todo56.dev. Thanks for translating!

paragraphs: TodoBot is a discord bot made with NodeJS using the discord.js library. It's mainly based on fun commands such as music, nsfw but it has also moderation features and administration too. This bot was first called AtomicBot and was focused in NSFW content, you can find the source code of this version here. The second release of the bot was better, introducing mysql for saving data such as warnings, guild information... This version was not very stable so it ended up being abandoned on my VPS still running until recently, the 1rst of November of 2019 when I started working on this Bot.

At the moment, the bot has only 8 categories (administration, developer, fun, information, moderation, nsfw, music and XP). If you have any suggestion for the bot please submit a suggestion form here or Direct-Message me on discord: Todo56#0001.
